00:33:54,860 --> 00:33:55,700
(Fan,)

585
00:33:56,160 --> 00:33:57,980
(I will take good care of Li.)

586
00:33:58,700 --> 00:33:59,540
(Don't worry.)

587
00:34:02,010 --> 00:34:03,780
(We will remember Fan)

588
00:34:04,270 --> 00:34:06,190
(and those who have passed.)

589
00:34:07,230 --> 00:34:10,990
♪Will not be in vain♪

590
00:34:14,060 --> 00:34:15,300
Since you left,

591
00:34:16,500 --> 00:34:18,700
I've never gotten lucky
when drawing grass straws.

592
00:34:20,020 --> 00:34:21,100
Today,

593
00:34:21,220 --> 00:34:22,500
we brought good wine

594
00:34:24,140 --> 00:34:25,060
to come and see you.

595
00:34:26,980 --> 00:34:27,820
Cheers.

596
00:34:28,380 --> 00:34:30,700
(Grave of Wei Liang)

597
00:34:31,540 --> 00:34:32,740
Xiaotao came too.

598
00:34:52,020 --> 00:34:54,380
This is the orchid you brought back.

599
00:34:57,020 --> 00:34:57,940
I water it

600
00:34:58,820 --> 00:35:00,260
and give it sun

601
00:35:00,980 --> 00:35:02,380
every day.

602
00:35:03,540 --> 00:35:05,540
It's growing well now.

603
00:35:07,660 --> 00:35:09,020
You're the kind of man

604
00:35:09,380 --> 00:35:10,980
who can't keep promises.

605
00:35:12,020 --> 00:35:12,860
See?

606
00:35:14,180 --> 00:35:15,880
In the end,
I'm the one bringing the orchid

607
00:35:15,880 --> 00:35:16,740
to propose to you.

608
00:35:23,620 --> 00:35:25,740
Whether you're alive or dead,

609
00:35:27,780 --> 00:35:30,060
I still want to marry you.

610
00:35:30,860 --> 00:35:34,060
(Grave of Wei Liang)

611
00:35:41,340 --> 00:35:42,860
In our hearts,

612
00:35:43,460 --> 00:35:44,620
these little weapons

613
00:35:44,780 --> 00:35:46,100
represent us.

614
00:35:47,060 --> 00:35:49,580
We weren't born on the same day

615
00:35:50,380 --> 00:35:51,340
and probably

616
00:35:51,540 --> 00:35:53,580
won't die on the same day.

617
00:35:55,220 --> 00:35:56,100
But one day,

618
00:35:57,140 --> 00:35:58,860
if we're all gone,

619
00:35:59,500 --> 00:36:01,100
with these weapons buried together,

620
00:36:02,020 --> 00:36:03,620
we'll always be brothers.

621
00:36:06,820 --> 00:36:07,700
Seeing it

622
00:36:08,300 --> 00:36:09,740
will be like seeing me.

623
00:36:15,460 --> 00:36:16,340
Is this a sign

624
00:36:16,620 --> 00:36:17,860
to stop fighting?

625
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:23,060
How did you manage to say that
in such a circumstance?

626
00:37:37,900 --> 00:37:38,740
Sir.

627
00:37:39,620 --> 00:37:40,700
Has the Lord been found?

628
00:37:40,900 --> 00:37:41,840
He's not at the office.

629
00:37:43,220 --> 00:37:44,060
Sir.

630
00:37:44,420 --> 00:37:45,360
Not the training ground.

631
00:37:46,900 --> 00:37:47,740
Sir.

632
00:37:48,620 --> 00:37:49,580
Lady Xu also said

633
00:37:49,580 --> 00:37:50,620
she hadn't seen the Lord.

634
00:37:51,440 --> 00:37:53,200
The deer offering ritual
is about to start.

635
00:37:53,200 --> 00:37:53,900
Without the Lord,

636
00:37:53,920 --> 00:37:55,220
how can the ritual be completed?

637
00:37:56,940 --> 00:37:58,060
Go fetch Lady Xu.

638
00:37:58,220 --> 00:38:00,300
Only she can accept the deer

639
00:38:00,300 --> 00:38:01,580
on behalf of the Lord.

640
00:38:01,740 --> 00:38:02,900
- Hurry.
- Yes.

641
00:38:10,940 --> 00:38:12,500
Don't cry.

642
00:38:14,420 --> 00:38:16,420
Stop crying.

643
00:38:18,660 --> 00:38:19,500
Don't cry.

644
00:38:23,580 --> 00:38:25,380
The ritual has started.

645
00:38:25,660 --> 00:38:26,940
Mr. Gongsun couldn't find you

646
00:38:26,940 --> 00:38:28,420
and brought Grandmother there.

647
00:38:28,700 --> 00:38:30,300
- Why are you here?
- Well.

648
00:38:30,300 --> 00:38:31,580
Feifei has been crying nonstop.

649
00:38:31,940 --> 00:38:33,780
I couldn't go.

650
00:38:35,740 --> 00:38:36,700
Alright.

651
00:38:36,900 --> 00:38:37,900
Good girl.

652
00:38:37,900 --> 00:38:39,540
Come on.

653
00:38:40,420 --> 00:38:41,260
Go to your mother.

654
00:38:42,020 --> 00:38:43,180
Don't cry.

655
00:38:45,260 --> 00:38:46,220
You're amazing.

656
00:38:53,260 --> 00:38:55,300
(Grandfather once compared
living a life)

657
00:38:55,300 --> 00:38:56,860
(to conquering the world.)

658
00:38:57,460 --> 00:38:58,700
(He said)

659
00:38:58,700 --> 00:39:00,740
(both required equal strength.)

660
00:39:01,260 --> 00:39:02,100
(Now,)

661
00:39:02,300 --> 00:39:03,460
(I think those words)

662
00:39:04,100 --> 00:39:05,740
(can be understood another way.)

663
00:39:06,860 --> 00:39:08,500
(Whether it's to live a life)

664
00:39:08,700 --> 00:39:10,060
(or conquer the world,)

665
00:39:10,780 --> 00:39:12,940
(both sides working together)

666
00:39:13,100 --> 00:39:14,900
(is the way to last.)

667
00:39:16,220 --> 00:39:18,100
(Luckily, my husband and I)

668
00:39:18,380 --> 00:39:19,980
(still understand)

669
00:39:20,340 --> 00:39:21,740
(and are devoted to each other)

670
00:39:21,900 --> 00:39:23,180
(after weathering many storms.)

671
00:39:24,540 --> 00:39:26,180
(He's willing to become my prisoner,)

672
00:39:27,100 --> 00:39:29,140
(and I'm willing to be his.)

673
00:39:43,220 --> 00:39:48,620
(Wei Mansion)

674
00:39:51,020 --> 00:39:52,140
(Years later,)

675
00:39:52,160 --> 00:39:53,920
(the Yongning Canal
brought huge benefits.)

676
00:39:54,260 --> 00:39:55,580
(The waterways are connected,)

677
00:39:55,580 --> 00:39:56,820
(benefiting all sides.)

678
00:39:57,380 --> 00:39:59,500
(The world is thus freed
from strife and hatred.)

679
00:39:59,940 --> 00:40:01,820
(The people are at peace.)

680
00:40:03,420 --> 00:40:05,260
(I've finally had
my lifelong wish come true)

681
00:40:05,860 --> 00:40:07,140
(by traveling with my wife)

682
00:40:07,420 --> 00:40:08,780
(to see the world.)

683
00:40:10,370 --> 00:40:13,130
(Thanks to the companions
on this journey.)

684
00:40:13,130 --> 00:40:14,520
(Everyone,)

685
00:40:14,520 --> 00:40:15,880
(in the years to come,)

686
00:40:16,260 --> 00:40:17,730
(may all your wishes come true.)

687
00:40:21,980 --> 00:40:25,180
(The end)

688
00:40:44,390 --> 00:40:47,220
♪The moonlight is as silent
as the deep sea♪

689
00:40:48,290 --> 00:40:50,750
♪From afar♪

690
00:40:52,700 --> 00:40:55,850
♪It once lit up dreams with a breath♪

691
00:40:56,770 --> 00:40:59,880
♪But vanished with a sigh♪

692
00:41:01,100 --> 00:41:04,470
♪Brushing past my fingertips♪

693
00:41:04,870 --> 00:41:08,240
♪My heartstrings were stirred quietly♪

694
00:41:09,070 --> 00:41:11,010
♪As if we once met before♪

695
00:41:11,500 --> 00:41:15,610
♪Holding back a love so deep♪

696
00:41:17,900 --> 00:41:21,270
♪Love asks for nothing in the end♪

697
00:41:21,860 --> 00:41:24,940
♪Leaving only obsessions♪

698
00:41:26,260 --> 00:41:29,660
♪I've wandered in the world♪

699
00:41:30,160 --> 00:41:33,160
♪Yet cannot have it all♪

700
00:41:34,720 --> 00:41:37,990
♪We meet and part in the fires of war♪

701
00:41:38,310 --> 00:41:42,000
♪Embracing,
leaving tender marks of love♪

702
00:41:42,700 --> 00:41:44,630
♪With one breathtaking glance♪

703
00:41:45,170 --> 00:41:50,090
♪How could I ever forget♪

704
00:41:50,670 --> 00:41:52,950
♪I would cross mountains and seas♪

705
00:41:52,950 --> 00:41:55,470
♪To spend time with you♪

706
00:41:55,720 --> 00:41:57,080
♪When we grow old♪

707
00:41:57,080 --> 00:41:59,670
♪Nothing will change♪

708
00:41:59,670 --> 00:42:01,270
♪The misty rains never cease♪

709
00:42:01,270 --> 00:42:04,130
♪Falling gently on your brow♪

710
00:42:04,130 --> 00:42:08,120
♪Lingering in my heart♪

711
00:42:08,120 --> 00:42:09,820
♪I would sever fate's ties♪

712
00:42:09,820 --> 00:42:12,240
♪To protect your smiling eyes♪

713
00:42:12,630 --> 00:42:16,500
♪Even if behind me lies a storm♪

714
00:42:16,500 --> 00:42:17,610
♪No matter the trials♪

